tiles will be 8x8 pixels and sprites will be max 16x16 pixels normal characters will be 8x16 probably

the game will be top down with a fixed orthagonal aspect ratio (like SD snatcher)

The scope of the game will be earth and space, with a focus on turn based combat when dealing with 1v1 or 4v1 taking inspiration from SD snatcher in that regard. Maybe also take some cues from Triagle strategy, because the combat will be mostly gun based with melee elements. 

Space travel should also be modelled and it should be possible to fly around in a war ship and also engage in combat. (turn based of course)


